         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Botanic Gardens 8/2/84. ¶ Sir. ¶ Having ¶ learned the ¶ decease of your second Assistant, Mr Groener, ¶ Groener died on 6 February; see M to G. Berry, 7 February 1884. ¶ I take the liberty of offering...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.02.08a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Charles French</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A84/1448, unit 21, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens 8/2/84.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Having<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">learned the</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>decease of your second Assistant, Mr Groener,</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Groener died on 6 February; see M to G. Berry, 7 February 1884.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I take the liberty of offering my services for the vacancy thus caused in your department.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As I have been employed under you during your directorship of the botanic Garden for a number of years and as you are<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>also otherwise sufficiently acquainted with my abilities I need not now refer to this subject specially, however if necessary I could supply testimonials also from other sources.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is is</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>is<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">repeated</seg>.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>nearly 20 years since I entered the service of the Government and at the present time I am in charge of the labelling Dpt in the Botanic Garden, my income at present is £150 per Annum and I occupy a 6 roomed cottage in the Gardens, free of rent, so that I should not be a gainer in a pecuniary respect, by this transfer, but the duties devolving upon me in your department, would be more in accord with my inclinations and I sincerely believe that I should give thorough satisfaction.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I now solicit therefore that you will kindly submit this my application to the Honorable the Chief Secretary for his favourable consideration.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles French.</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles French Snr.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M forwarded the application, which was duly approved; see M to G. Berry, 9 February<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1884 (in this edition as 84-02-09a), and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>T. Wilson to M, 14 March 1884.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir F. Von Mueller, K.C.M.G. &amp;c</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
